Exception and Resource

Exception and Resource

Consider the following function

int fibo(int n) {
    int *a = new int[n+2];
    if(n &gt; 46) throw "overflow";
    a[0] = 1; 
    a[1] = 1;   
    for(int i=2; i&lt;=n; i++) a[i] = a[i-1] + a[i-2];
    int re = a[n];
    delete[] a;
    return re;
